name: The Five Eyes 10,781
description:
artonomous portrait of The Five Eyes,
a bitGAN created from the burning of
bitGANs (0o16) and (0o17). This
portrait was painted by an AI enabled
robot with 10,781 brushstrokes. It is a
mystery why the bitGANs have
suddenly begun appearing, though it
appears that they are trying to tell us
something important.
